{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">DRFT is an arcade topdown roguelite where drifting makes you stronger! A clever balance between controlling your drifting car and steering clear from masses of enemies. Use your weapons and abilities to clear massive waves of enemies or skillfully evade them by drifting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968670/extras/gameplay_header.png?t=1738329622\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968670/extras/drft_transparent_gif_01.gif?t=1738329622\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gameplay\u00a0</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can't brake!, steer left and right and use the walls to bounce around!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your weapons attack automatically when close to enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine upgrades to increase the power and utility of your weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clearing waves of enemies grants upgrades, which can be used to empower your car and weapons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968670/extras/upgrade-title.png?t=1738329622\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968670/extras/drft_pickup_rewards.gif?t=1738329622\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features\u00a0</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10+ weapons, each with unique attacks and utility</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">12+ enemies, each varying in strength and behavior</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">endless levels of increasing difficulty and fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">15+ Steam achievements</p></li></ul